node.text:
THE VERTICAL DIET hard copy will be in Barnes & Noble Aug 10th and is now available for pre-order on Amazon. 
.
Co-authored by Damon McCune PhD, RDN, LD @drdamonmccune 
.
Damon and I have received over 100,000 DM’s, emails and messages from vertical diet users all over the world with Questions, comments, Kudo’s and yes, even some complaints, which we’ve used to continue to expand upon and update The Vertical Diet to help as many people as possible achieve their health and fitness goals. 
.
Victory Belt Publishing has done an outstanding job with the quality of this book and we’re excited to share it with you!!
.
Please be sure to let us know what you think. Thank you!!

.

#Repost @jonnybones with @make_repost
・・・
Knowledge is power and you’re not going to want to miss this one! Encouraging all athletes and trainers in the surrounding areas to come and check out this amazing seminar! Hope to see you there.

👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇

.

.
8 Coaches, 8 Hours AND a special guest appearance by the GOAT 🐐 @jonnybones.
.
✅ Vertical Diet Coaches Certification

.

THE VERTICAL DIET hard copy will be in Barnes & Noble Aug 10th and is now available for pre-order on Amazon. 
.
Co-authored by Damon McCune PhD, RDN, LD @drdamonmccune 
.
Damon and I have received over 100,000 DM’s, emails and messages from vertical diet users all over the world with Questions, comments, Kudo’s and yes, even some complaints, which we’ve used to continue to expand upon and update The Vertical Diet to help as many people as possible achieve their health and fitness goals. 
.
Victory Belt Publishing has done an outstanding job with the quality of this book and we’re excited to share it with you!!
.
Please be sure to let us know what you think. Thank you!!

Etc. saw so many nurses and chiropractors to help thought cortisone injections in the neck and manipulations would cure it. It turned out it made things worse. Salt!! Adding iodized salt took care of it!! God bless you, Stan!! And thanks again for all of your help.'.

node.text:
Yep, salt “works”!!
.
If you’re overweight, hypertensive, sedentary and eating fast food and Pringle’s, don’t add salt. Duh!!
.
If you’re active and eating Whole Foods (avoiding fast food and packaged foods), adding salt can improve your workout stamina and endurance. 
.
I cover it all in “The Vertical Diet 3.0” ebook along with links to over 200 videos, articles and peer reviewed published research. 
.
Full Youtube interview with @metabolic_mike at High Intensity Health.
